column5: Just been watching Oasis in concert on SunTV in HD     Live at Tweeter Centre in Boston  I'm not a fan of all their songs, but I do like a fair few of them.  Just flipping channels and it was on and its not bad at all.  Just an FYI if you're an Oasis fan.  Joey
